{"parse": {"title": "Lance Hardy", "pageid": 30654, "text": {"*": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><div class=\"eraicon filtericon\"><span typeof=\"mw:File\"><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\"><img alt=\"2077Icon\" src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/7/77/2077Icon.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/80?cb=20180612180205\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"80\" height=\"20\" class=\"mw-file-element\" data-image-name=\"2077Icon.png\" data-image-key=\"2077Icon.png\" data-relevant=\"1\" /></a></span></div>\n<div class=\"divTable bannercurve\"><div style=\"vertical-align:middle;\"><i>Our community <a href=\"/wiki/Category:Article_stubs\" title=\"Category:Article stubs\">needs more</a> information on this page! Can you help out? <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Lance_Hardy?action=edit\">Click here to add more.</a></i></div></div>\n<p>\n<aside role=\"region\" class=\"portable-infobox pi-background pi-border-color pi-theme-wikia pi-layout-default\">\n<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-item-spacing pi-title pi-secondary-background\" data-source=\"title\">Lance Hardy</h2>\n\n<figure class=\"pi-item pi-image\" data-source=\"image\">\n\t<a href=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/84/Lance_Hardy_Infobox_CP2077.png/revision/latest?cb=20230916082148\" class=\"image image-thumbnail\" title=\"Lance Hardy Infobox CP2077\">\n\t\t<img src=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/84/Lance_Hardy_Infobox_CP2077.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20230916082148\" srcset=\"https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/84/Lance_Hardy_Infobox_CP2077.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/268?cb=20230916082148 1x, https://static.wikia.nocookie.net/cyberpunk/images/8/84/Lance_Hardy_Infobox_CP2077.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/536?cb=20230916082148 2x\" class=\"pi-image-thumbnail\" data-relevant=\"1\" alt=\"Lance Hardy Infobox CP2077\" width=\"270\" height=\"360\" data-image-key=\"Lance_Hardy_Infobox_CP2077.png\" data-image-name=\"Lance Hardy Infobox CP2077.png\" />\n\t\t\n\t</a>\n\t\n</figure>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Biographical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"status\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Status</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Dependent</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"dod\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Date of Death</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/2077\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"2077\">2077</a> (dependent)</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"place_of_death\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Place of Death</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><a href=\"/wiki/Downtown\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Downtown\">Downtown</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/City_Center_(2077)\" title=\"City Center (2077)\">City Center</a> (dependent)</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Physical Information</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"gender\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Gender</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Male</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"hair_color\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Hair Color</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Black</div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"eyes\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Eye Color</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\">Hazel</div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n<section class=\"pi-item pi-group pi-border-color pi-collapse pi-collapse-closed\">\n\t<h2 class=\"pi-item pi-header pi-secondary-font pi-item-spacing pi-secondary-background\">Appearances</h2>\n\n<div class=\"pi-item pi-data pi-item-spacing pi-border-color\" data-source=\"appears_games\">\n\t\n\t\t<h3 class=\"pi-data-label pi-secondary-font\">Game(s)</h3>\n\t\n\t<div class=\"pi-data-value pi-font\"><i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i></div>\n</div>\n\n</section>\n</aside>\n\n<b>Lance Hardy</b> is a character in <i><a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077\">Cyberpunk 2077</a></i>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Biography\">Biography</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FLance_Hardy%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D1&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"divTable bannercurve\"><i>This section requires expanding. <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Lance_Hardy?action=edit\">Click here to add more.</a></i><a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"text\" href=\"https://cyberpunk.fandom.com/wiki/Lance_Hardy?action=edit\">\ud83d\udcdd</a></div>\n<p>Lance is met during one of the <a href=\"/wiki/Cyberpunk_2077_NCPD_Scanner_Hustles\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Cyberpunk 2077 NCPD Scanner Hustles\">Assaults in Progress</a> in <a href=\"/wiki/Downtown\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Downtown\">Downtown</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/City_Center_(2077)\" title=\"City Center (2077)\">City Center</a>. He is one of the merc hired to get rid of <a href=\"/wiki/Manuel_Mendoza\" title=\"Manuel Mendoza\">Manuel Mendoza</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Associated_Shards\">Associated Shards</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a title=\"Sign in to edit\" class=\"mw-editsection-visualeditor\" data-tracking-label=\"log-in-edit-section\" data-action=\"edit-section\" href=\"https://auth.fandom.com/signin?redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fcyberpunk.fandom.com%2Fwiki%2FLance_Hardy%3Fveaction%3Dedit%26section%3D2&amp;uselang=en\" data-testid=\"log-in-edit-section\"><svg class=\"wds-icon wds-icon-tiny\"><use xlink:href=\"#wds-icons-pencil-tiny\"></use></svg></a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Archived_Conversation:_Major_Lance_Hardy_and_Mark_Caroll\" title=\"Archived Conversation: Major Lance Hardy and Mark Caroll\">Archived Conversation: Major Lance Hardy and Mark Caroll</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/wiki/Notes_(Downtown)\" title=\"Notes (Downtown)\">Notes (Downtown)</a></li></ul></div>"}, "images": ["Lance_Hardy_Infobox_CP2077.png", "2077Icon.png"]}}